# Biometric Attendance Management System

- [x] Project Initialization
  - [x] Set up NestJS backend project in `backend` folder
  - [x] Configure PostgreSQL database connection using Prisma ORM
  - [x] Set up environment variables and basic configuration
- [ ] Database Schema Design
  - [ ] Create `Device` model
  - [ ] Create `User` mapping model (System ID to Device ID)
  - [ ] Create `RawLog` model for device sync logs
  - [ ] Create `ProcessedAttendance` model
  - [ ] Create University specific models (Periods, Subjects, Enrollments)
- [ ] Device Management Module
  - [ ] API for CRUD operations on devices
  - [ ] Device connection test API
  - [ ] Device status monitoring (Online/Offline)
- [ ] Log Sync Module
  - [ ] API for manual log upload (USB/File)
  - [ ] Webhook for real-time push logs
  - [ ] Background scheduler (Cron) for pulling logs via TCP/IP
  - [ ] Store logs in `RawLog` table securely
- [ ] Attendance Processing Engine
  - [ ] Background job to process new `RawLog` entries
  - [ ] Implement fraud prevention (duplicate scans, time manipulation)
  - [ ] Handle daily status updates (Present, Late, Absent)
  - [ ] Period/Subject-based attendance logic for universities
- [ ] Admin & Reporting APIs
  - [ ] Fetch attendance with filters (campus, date, student, etc.)
  - [ ] Export daily/monthly attendance to PDF
  - [ ] Real-time alerts (Offline device, low attendance)
- [ ] Authentication & Security
  - [ ] JWT role-based access control
  - [ ] API security guards

